name: Qatar Airways Business Class Qsuite A350-1000
description:
Qatar Airways Business Class has been described to me as being so good, you don’t need First Class. In fact, it’s been one of the most requested videos by subscribers to this channel.

In this video, we’ll highlight all it has to offer on a 12+ hour flight from Dulles to Doha. From the lounge in Washington, DC to the Qatar Airways Business Class Qsuite seat itself, the Qatar Airways Business Class food, the Oryx One Inflight Entertainment, and the Qatar Airways Business Class Service, you’ll see it all!

This flight is the first episode of our #NewlywedWorldTour! We’re two tremendous aviation enthusiasts, and, in order to celebrate our honeymoon, we strung together several ultimate aviation experiences into one African adventure that took us from the United States to Kenya, the Seychelles, and Egypt. 

This Qatar Airways Business Class flight onboard the A350-1000 will go down in our “logbooks” as one of our favorite flights. And there are a lot of reasons for it, so I hope you’ll enjoy the video from beginning to end!

And be sure to let us know what you think in the comments below. We read every one!

0:00 Introduction
0:53 Dulles – Doha Flight Overview
